        <font color="midnightblue" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> Well we aren't just lookign for untagged bodies, but I know thats not what you meant. If you are adventuring and meet some really nice people who aren't in a guild you are welcome to send them to our application page. Any questions you aren't sure about or aren't comfortable answering can be handled by an officer in game or he can give them an email address. Far as I know LOA hasn't stopped recruiting in Dark Ages, last I left, we were still growing and not nearly done!</P><P><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
